neg-lookbehind.description: Starting at the current position in the expression, ensures that the given pattern will not match. Does not consume characters.

neg-lookahead.description: Ensures that the given pattern would not match and end at the current position in the expression. Does not consume characters.

pos-look-behind.description: Ensures that the given pattern will match, ending at the current position in the expression. Does not consume any characters.

pos-look-ahead.description: Matches the given subpattern without consuming characters
